  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/c8b879ab85f7905ac82a2b95f6ccf614.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Race with Hide and seek</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat the cake before your friends without getting spotted !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not just a simple race, be careful and strategize to arrive first</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A main party game mode to play with your friends, featuring Robots to blend in and a sauce you control to eliminate your friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/445214d67cc92df370e7800d255febb2.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect delicious cakes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cake collection view to see and collect all the cakes you encounter during your games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 cakes to collect and learn more about them, associated with achievements !</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/d98fcde959bf9e8093ffe7f36d88878f.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Various sub and fun modes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 main sub-modes to vary gameplay, as well as many other small tweaks in Chaos mode !</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/284b3cb29d8004c616447b9742af7d19.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2 to 4 player local party game</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 4 players locally or online with steam remote play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need only one copy of the game to invite up to 3 friends and play together online via steam !</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/e329fa69d18fca97b839bd34f8ad0944.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span><strong>Made with love</strong>  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made by a small indie team of only 3 people ❤️</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/c8b879ab85f7905ac82a2b95f6ccf614.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Race with Hide and seek</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat the cake before your friends without getting spotted !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not just a simple race, be careful and strategize to arrive first</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A main party game mode to play with your friends, featuring Robots to blend in and a sauce you control to eliminate your friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/445214d67cc92df370e7800d255febb2.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect delicious cakes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cake collection view to see and collect all the cakes you encounter during your games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 cakes to collect and learn more about them, associated with achievements !</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/d98fcde959bf9e8093ffe7f36d88878f.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Various sub and fun modes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 main sub-modes to vary gameplay, as well as many other small tweaks in Chaos mode !</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/284b3cb29d8004c616447b9742af7d19.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2 to 4 player local party game</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 4 players locally or online with steam remote play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need only one copy of the game to invite up to 3 friends and play together online via steam !</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884670/extras/e329fa69d18fca97b839bd34f8ad0944.avif?t=1748063489\" width=616 height=157 /></span><strong>Made with love</strong>  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made by a small indie team of only 3 people ❤️</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
